<event name="AET_FUEL_TRADE_A_LIFE">   
	<text>A slug ship approaches you. You hear them say "Perhpassss we can help you, for the modreatate price of a life. We need it for expirements. We have lots of fuelssss..."</text>
	<choice>
		<text>Give them a random crew member for fuel.</text>
		<event>
			<text>You give up one off your crewmembers for fuel. It seems that their experiments have delayed the fleet. You try to forget the hideous fate of yout beloved friend.</text>
			<crewMember amount="-1"/>
			<modifyPursuit amount="-1"/>
			<item_modify>
				<item type="scrap" min="-15" max="-15"/>
				<item type="fuel" min="5" max="15"/>
			</item_modify>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice>
		<text>Tell them that you won't offer a crewmember for the sake of the ship.</text>
		<event>
			<text>Angered the slugs sends out a signal that points the fleet to your position.</text>
			<modifyPursuit amount="1"/>
		</event>
	</choice>
</event>